output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: No CMF number is present, but this doesn't automatically disqualify it as propaganda.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes, explicitly mentions multiple presidential candidates: - Nicolae Ciucă (PNL) - Marcel Ciolacu (PSD) - George Simion (AUR) - Elena Lasconi (USR) - Ludovic Orban (Forța Dreptei)
3. Addresses wide population: Yes, this is a paid Facebook post with significant reach (125,000-150,000 impressions).
4. Electoral objective: Yes, very clearly: - Directly attempts to influence Ciucă to withdraw his candidacy - Promotes Elena Lasconi as the viable right-wing alternative - Tries to influence voter perception about candidates' chances - Suggests specific electoral alliances and outcomes
5. Journalism: No, this is clearly a political message, not journalistic content.
6. Personal opinion: While presented as Orban's opinion, the paid promotion and clear electoral objectives make this electoral propaganda.
The post clearly aims to influence the presidential election by: - Discouraging votes for Ciucă - Promoting votes for Lasconi - Warning against Ciolacu and Simion - Attempting to influence electoral alliances

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This constitutes electoral propaganda because: - It directly addresses multiple presidential candidates - Has clear electoral objectives - Is widely distributed through paid promotion - Attempts to influence voting behavior - Makes specific electoral predictions and recommendations
conclusion.message-for-police: WEBASSIST CONSULTING SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin promovarea unui mesaj de propaganda electorala (ID postare Facebook: 923407932626906) dupa incheierea perioadei de campanie electorala, respectiv dupa ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Mesajul promovat contine elemente clare de propaganda electorala, incluzand indemnuri directe de vot pentru candidatul Elena Lasconi, descurajarea votului pentru Nicolae Ciuca, precum si avertizari negative despre Marcel Ciolacu si George Simion. Postarea, promovata prin plata, a ajuns la un public de 125.000-150.000 persoane, demonstrand caracterul sau de comunicare electorala in masa. Efectul electoral urmarit este clar: redirectionarea voturilor de la un candidat la altul si influentarea rezultatului alegerilor prezidentiale prin sugestii explicite de vot.
